To announce to OMPI core testers:

- Default number of lines saved (for stdout and stderr) in phases is
  100; it used to be 1000. 
- INI file used to have "separate_stdout_stderr" as a field; this has
  been renamed to "merge_stdout_stderr".
- New MPI Details after_each_exec section to do cleanup on all nodes.
- New details for Simple Test Run specification in INI file
  - can allow some tests to fail
  - see new section in ompi-core-template.ini
